| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2344 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0475dcb1-f29f-5dff-814a-dfb32f1b0bf7"
